about:
The Mike Tyson NFT Collection is a limited-edition series of NFTs that 
celebrates the iconic life and legacy of the Baddest Man on the Planet, Mike Tyson. 
Each NFT is a unique collaboration between Mike Tyson and emerging artist Cory Van Lew. 
With Mike providing creative oversight and mentorship in the artistic process, 
The Mike Tyson NFT Collection is Cory Van Lew’s reimagination and interpretation of 
the all-time greatest Mike Tyson moments and images.

The Mike Tyson NFT Collection Includes:

The Ultimate Mike Tyson 1-of-1 NFT (1-of-1)

The Lifetime Collection (A limited set of 10 original 1-of-1 NFTs)

The Knockout Series (A limited set of 5 original NFTs - limited to 50 editions each)

The Baddest Man on the Planet (A single collector's edition NFT with 250 editions)
